cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a novel approach for image denoising by minimizing the rank residual, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and image processing (cs.MM). The proposed method also involves integrating image nonlocal self-similarity (NSS) prior, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also provides a theoretical analysis of the proposed model, which is related to signal processing (cs.SI).
